father's mistress.

15:29.232 --> 15:30.433
God, parents. Right?

15:30.434 --> 15:34.303
Again, just a whole
other thing, sweetie.

15:34.304 --> 15:35.871
Where'd they go?

15:35.872 --> 15:37.907
