objective, but...

17:00.023 --> 17:03.325
The truth is, I...

17:03.326 --> 17:05.461
I loved growing up here.

17:07.196 --> 17:09.298
We had just moved to New York.

17:09.299 --> 17:11.934
We were completely broke.

17:11.935 --> 17:14.737
